---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Work/Life | Implementation Guide" description="A practical guide to implementing the 4-day workweek in your organization." active="implementation">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-end">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container rounded-full text-xs font-bold tracking-widest mb-6 uppercase">THE MANUAL</span>
        <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light tracking-tight text-on-surface leading-[1.1]">
          From Theory to <br />
          <span class="italic font-medium text-primary">Transformation</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Transitioning to a more human pace isn't just an organizational shift&mdash;it's a cultural metamorphosis. Discover the architectural blueprints for a modern workday.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] shadow-xl">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Modern office studio" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBz_i2XjQcd5q0lE2gLNlqOz6R-MynXqzJ3lB9sW8N8rHVFvKtNQ9tMBP8or3ZUM0s7XmkLj77M2qiJrN4TN11HEhN2kieLb96eAXK0KHRjAUGffWKO_-GOwgwSHtv5YUo7sDjr9BUhWY260OFJj7p1kz9rskapuRKvyS_UonckcQoc3Crm_XJ03uTpKg_r9QyRP8ZQZZdw30Eda7FNHREI8Qi0tU458b6yTKkB2bUx0dYYS0kauBAnfHkojR5slkURFCJvegB_Y98" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Readiness Roadmap -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl mb-4">Readiness Roadmap</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-tertiary-container"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      {[
        { num: "01", icon: "search", title: "Audit the Flow", desc: "Map current energy cycles, task density, and meeting load. Identify productivity 'choke points' and time sinks that compress into 4 days." },
        { num: "02", icon: "architecture", title: "Design the Model", desc: "Choose your approach: 4x10 compressed, 4x8 reduced hours (100-80-100 model), flexible/hybrid, or staggered schedules." },
        { num: "03", icon: "groups", title: "Align the Team", desc: "Communicate expectations clearly. Andrew Barnes says: 'Gift it, don't mandate it.' Build trust and empower teams to own the process." },
        { num: "04", icon: "auto_awesome", title: "Iterate & Measure", desc: "Run a 3-6 month pilot. Track productivity, wellbeing, and revenue. 92% of UK pilot companies continued permanently." },
      ].map((step) => (
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
          <span class="absolute -right-4 -top-4 font-headline text-8xl text-surface-container opacity-50 group-hover:text-tertiary-container transition-colors">{step.num}</span>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-container rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary-container">{step.icon}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-3">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">{step.desc}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Implementation Strategies Bento -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 grid-rows-2 gap-6 h-auto md:h-[600px]">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl mb-4">The Deep Work Anchor</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6">Reserve the first 90 minutes for high-cognition tasks. This is the foundation of making 4 days as productive as 5.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span>Zero-notification environment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span>Eliminate unnecessary meetings</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mt-1">check_circle</span>
              <span>Async-first communication</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden grayscale-[0.3] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Clean desk for deep work" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCtGwUMYIsPgtCh6ZQ76XC3Eb9GlvWM4qMaFtrbTMKwIEhcPibXTgzFu5JBbYpfrAWyzanxTrwyjCsRHnC9obibHP5_5W4gz6dK184e26IXHU70bRxBKM-FDq_Ju-65chgN-Vt1jrzYD03tv6T4FShXdKgpDRXTfKJ845QYj_Sq_XmSoTuQSdcWhp6gvgqMnGuCrbAWWHNpRKbY0Lt1ujZqvl-03QWipN0rnwDrrBj-NtSNSlH8LYcsNxLYMl7amLqDao14zPpRBs4" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-1 bg-tertiary-container/30 p-8 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-2">The 100-80-100 Model</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-tertiary-container">100% pay, 80% time, 100% productivity. The most widely adopted model, proven across tech, finance, government, and manufacturing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:flex w-32 h-32 rounded-full border-4 border-dashed border-tertiary/20 items-center justify-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-tertiary">timer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-1 bg-surface-container p-8 rounded-xl">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-4" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">format_quote</span>
        <p class="font-headline italic text-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">"Gift it, don't mandate it. Trust your people to find the best way."</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-3">&mdash; Andrew Barnes, Perpetual Guardian</p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-1 bg-primary text-on-primary p-8 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-center text-center">
        <span class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold mb-1">92%</span>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold opacity-80">Companies Continue</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 font-light">UK pilot firms kept the 4-day week after the trial ended.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Countering the Skeptics -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl mb-4">Countering the Skeptics</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant italic">Common objections, addressed with evidence.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="font-headline text-xl text-primary md:w-1/3">"Productivity will drop."</div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Microsoft Japan saw +40% productivity. The US/Ireland pilot reported +38% revenue growth. Across 60+ pilots, not a single company reported meaningful productivity loss.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-secondary">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="font-headline text-xl text-secondary md:w-1/3">"Not all industries can do it."</div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Healthcare, manufacturing, finance, government, and retail have all found creative solutions&mdash;from staggered shifts to rotating schedules. Belgium made it law across all sectors.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-tertiary">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="font-headline text-xl text-tertiary md:w-1/3">"Clients need us 5 days."</div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Staggered schedules maintain 5-day coverage with 4-day individual weeks. Perpetual Guardian proved clients don't notice when service quality stays constant.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-error">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="font-headline text-xl text-error md:w-1/3">"It's just a fad."</div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            We went from 6-day to 5-day weeks a century ago. Working hours have dropped 34% since the Industrial Revolution. This is the next step in a 200-year trend toward more humane work.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Callout -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-20">
    <div class="bg-secondary-container p-12 rounded-[2rem] flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute -left-12 -bottom-12 w-64 h-64 bg-on-secondary-container opacity-5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 md:w-1/2">
        <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl text-on-secondary-container mb-6">Ready to redesign your rhythm?</h3>
        <p class="text-on-secondary-container/80 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Explore our research, share it with your team, and start the conversation about what a more human workweek looks like for your organization.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-on-secondary-container text-secondary-container px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:scale-[1.05] transition-transform">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
          Back to The Movement
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 md:w-1/2 aspect-video bg-surface-container-lowest/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-on-secondary-container/10 p-4 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-on-secondary-container/30">auto_stories</span>
          <p class="text-on-secondary-container mt-4 font-medium italic">The evidence for a more human pace of work</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
